css-selectors CHANGES
=====================

Version 1.0.3

Scanner:

 * Fixed issue where the last selectors were added twice to the selector groups. I.e.
   the last selectors were checked twice and caused unnecessary tree walking.

Version 1.0.2
-------------

Pseudo-classes:

 * Added support for the :root pseudo-class fixed by hakos.

Version 1.0.1-SNAPSHOT
----------------------

Combinators:

 * Fixed a bug where the General Sibling Combinator handling only returned the first match found.
 
